title: Beatles - Having Fun In Get Back Sessions
description:
3 CD Collection from the Get Back sessions in 1969.
Jaming old songs and composing new material for LET IT BE and ABBEY ROAD.

Highlights are Lennon taking the lead of McCartney songs and his powerful version of Dont Let Me Down and Across The Universe.


Opposit to other collections there is no endless boring takes of the same song.


This is in fact a joyful performance by Beatles performing old favorites and having fun
